snippet.title: CRAVEN Something Scary
snippet.description:
Hey everyone this is Stephen! Welcome to my “Craven Something Scary” YouTube channel where I dive in to all things Wes Craven and also horror and thriller films in general. I am focused primarily on doing Updates, reactions, reviews and discussion videos. Sometimes I’m joined by special guests and other times it’s just YOU AND ME!

This is no fun without you, so be sure and subscribe to my channel right now and hit that bell icon to be notified when all of my video content goes live! I look forward to hearing from you in the comments and talking Wes Craven and horror films with you! Thanks for watching!

Visit my social media pages below!

	Twitter: https://twitter.com/cravenmovies

	Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/cravensomethingscary/

	Face Book: www.facebook.com/cravensomethingscary

	YouTube Channel: www.cravensomethingscary.com
